# Important: These native files SHOULD be committed
# - android/app/src/main/res/ (app icons and resources)
# - windows/runner/resources/ (app icons)
# - windows/runner/*.cpp, *.h (native Windows code)
# - lib/statics/ (app assets like logo.png)
# - Any custom assets defined in pubspec.yaml

